I have always been passionate about data-driven decision-making and AI-powered automation to accelerate growth, and envision myself contributing my talent to the furthering of Flywheel's mission to help the world's leading brands grow faster, smarter, and more efficiently in digital commerce. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

